rows.name:
It's night, so Magomago can
play with Grampypon, mo! I'm
sleepy, but I'm happy, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100181_03_msg0003
rows.name:
You know, Grampypon is friends
with the big shots here, mo! That's
why he could bring goods, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100181_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Ahem, ahem! Magomago is going to
become a merchant like Grampypon, mo!
